frameDefinitions: A Supplier gives a Theme to a Recipient to fulfill a need or purpose (Imposed_purpose) of the Recipient.
A Supply of a Resource is kept safe and available for a future Use.
These are words relating to filling containers and covering areas with some thing, things or substance, the Theme.
A Material is used to make a Product.
Lexical units in this frame refer to Electricity, in particular as a form of energy harnessed for particular uses (such as powering machines).

<fen>Electricity</fen> is the physical force that is used as power.
